ian lifestyles leave me a little anemic and when I underwent this kind of low last year it was just after going off iron, which itself was irritating my colon and preventing uptake of other essential nutrients. I've always had crazy iron issues.  Whether through time or diet or a good friend, I'm happy to say I'm feeling better. All I need now is a good sunburn and I'll be cured. I'd better get it before hurricane Bonnie and her friend Charlie come to shore!
     
    
