erday so I turned and walked out. No crying haunted me as I walked down the hallway, I didn't have to hide in the foyer and send in someone to see if he's ok now. It felt great!  If only Ellie felt great, too. She seems to be under the weather, is pretty unhappy, spits up big amounts of her food at once right after eating. She hasn't gotten rid of her runny nose from last week yet either. I need to eat some good garlic and green chile to up her immune system. It tears me up when she's sick, that sad little sneeze and runny face!
     
    
